Toggle pacman sync and upgrade with immutable chattr.

How to Install on Linux Machine

Steps:
1. Clone this repository:
   git clone https://github.com/bydzen/paclock.git
2. Enter the directory:
   cd packlock/
3. Copy main file to binary:
   sudo cp paclock /usr/bin/
4. Make executable:
   sudo chmod +x /usr/bin/paclock

Usage:
paclock [options]
Options:
  lock      Toggle chattr +i on /var/lib/pacman/local
  unlock    Toggle chattr -i on /var/lib/pacman/local
  status    Check if /var/lib/pacman/local is locked or unlocked

Help:
paclock

Enjoy.
